.SH LXD ARCHITECTURE
LXD provides system containers that offer:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Full Linux system environment in isolated containers
.IP \(bu 2
Near-native performance (no virtualization overhead)
.IP \(bu 2
Instant startup times (containers start in seconds)
.IP \(bu 2
Efficient resource usage (shared kernel with host)
.IP \(bu 2
Network isolation and management
.IP \(bu 2
Storage management with various backends
.IP \(bu 2
Snapshot and backup capabilities
.IP \(bu 2
Live migration support between hosts
.RE
